  7  /-!
  8  # Order for Rational Numbers
  9  
 10  ## Summary
 11  
 12  We define the order on `ℚ`, prove that `ℚ` is a discrete, linearly ordered field, and define
 13  functions such as `abs` and `sqrt` that depend on this order.
 14  
 15  ## Notations
 16  
 17  - `/.` is infix notation for `rat.mk`.
 18  
 19  ## Tags
 20  
 21  rat, rationals, field, ℚ, numerator, denominator, num, denom, order, ordering, sqrt, abs
 22  -/
